## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of sources that specifically address the role of research in daily life. Some sources may offer generalized insights rather than specific applications. Additionally, the reliance on online sources may introduce bias, as not all perspectives or regions may be equally represented. Further research could include more diverse sources, such as academic journals or expert interviews, to provide a more comprehensive view.

